---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: "Free Digital Readiness Audit — NorthHead Digital"
description: "Book a free 30-minute Digital & AI Readiness Audit. Serving Long Beach, Ilwaco, Ocean Park, Astoria, and coastal small businesses across the Pacific Northwest."
canonical: "https://northheaddigital.com/contact.html"
ogTitle: "Free Digital Readiness Audit — NorthHead Digital"
ogDescription: "Book a free 30-minute Digital & AI Readiness Audit for your coastal small business."
active: contact
permalink: /contact.html
---
<main id="main">
    <section class="page-hero">
      <div class="container">
        <span class="eyebrow text-sand">Free 30-minute consultation</span>
        <h1>Schedule a Digital &amp; AI Readiness Audit</h1>
        <p>The goal isn't to sell you technology. It's to understand how customers find you, where you lose time, and where you may be missing easy business — and you'll leave with a clear summary either way.</p>
        <p class="page-hero-area">Serving Long Beach, Ilwaco, Ocean Park, Seaview, Chinook, Astoria, and coastal small businesses across the Pacific Northwest.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="split">
          <!-- Left: what to expect -->
          <div class="reveal">
            <span class="eyebrow">What to expect</span>
            <h2>A calm, plain-language conversation</h2>
            <p>In about 30 minutes we'll walk through your online presence and day-to-day operations, then summarize the top opportunities.</p>
            <ul class="feature-list">
              <li><strong>Visibility</strong> — how easily customers find you on Google and mobile</li>
              <li><strong>Conversion</strong> — how easy it is to call, book, or request a quote</li>
              <li><strong>Operations</strong> — repeat questions and manual follow-up costing you time</li>
            </ul>
            <p class="mt-md">Prefer email? Reach us at
              <a href="mailto:hello@northheaddigital.com">hello@northheaddigital.com</a>.
            </p>
            <blockquote class="pull mt-lg">"Would you like a simple proposal with the exact scope, price, and timeline?"</blockquote>
          </div>

          <!-- Right: form -->
          <div class="reveal">
            <div class="form-card">
              <!--
                Netlify Forms compatible: the data-netlify attribute + hidden
                form-name input enable capture on Netlify with no backend.
                The honeypot field deters spam. main.js handles submission UX.
              -->
              <form name="audit-request" method="POST" data-netlify="true" netlify-honeypot="bot-field" data-contact>
                <input type="hidden" name="form-name" value="audit-request" />
                <p hidden><label>Don't fill this out: <input name="bot-field" /></label></p>

                <div class="field-row">
                  <div class="field">
                    <label for="business">Business name</label>
                    <input type="text" id="business" name="business" autocomplete="organization" required />
                  </div>
                  <div class="field">
                    <label for="name">Your name</label>
                    <input type="text" id="name" name="name" autocomplete="name" required />
                  </div>
                </div>

                <div class="field-row">
                  <div class="field">
                    <label for="email">Email</label>
                    <input type="email" id="email" name="email" autocomplete="email" required />
                  </div>
                  <div class="field">
                    <label for="phone">Phone <span class="optional-label">(optional)</span></label>
                    <input type="tel" id="phone" name="phone" autocomplete="tel" />
                  </div>
                </div>

                <div class="field-row">
                  <div class="field">
                    <label for="industry">Type of business</label>
                    <select id="industry" name="industry" required>
                      <option value="" disabled selected>Choose one…</option>
                      <option>Restaurant / cafe</option>
                      <option>Hotel / inn / lodging</option>
                      <option>Retail shop</option>
                      <option>Contractor / trades</option>
                      <option>Service business</option>
                      <option>New business / launch</option>
                      <option>Other</option>
                    </select>
                  </div>
                  <div class="field">
                    <label for="goal">Main goal right now</label>
                    <select id="goal" name="goal" required>
                      <option value="" disabled selected>Choose one…</option>
                      <option>More calls or walk-ins</option>
                      <option>More bookings or quote requests</option>
                      <option>Better Google visibility</option>
                      <option>Recover missed leads</option>
                      <option>Save time on repetitive work</option>
                      <option>A new or refreshed website</option>
                    </select>
                  </div>
                </div>

                <div class="field">
                  <label for="message">Anything you'd like us to know? <span class="optional-label">(optional)</span></label>
                  <textarea id="message" name="message" placeholder="Tell us a little about your business and what's frustrating you online."></textarea>
                </div>

                <button type="submit" class="btn btn--primary btn--lg btn--full">Request my free audit</button>
                <p class="form-status" role="status" aria-live="polite"></p>
                <p class="note note--form">No pressure, no obligation. We typically respond within one business day.</p>
              </form>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
